The 2017 Bojangles' Southern 500, the 68th running of the event, is a Monster Energy NASCAR Cup Series race held on September 3, 2017 at Darlington Raceway in Darlington, South Carolina. Contested over 367 laps on the 1.366-mile (2.198 km) egg-shaped oval, it is the 25th race of the 2017 Monster Energy NASCAR Cup Series season.
